ent/uploads/2021/09/17151126/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-top-clean--120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/17151126/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-top-clean--768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/17151103/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-clean-crankset-.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/17151103/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-clean-crankset-.jpg\" alt=\"Lars Forster Scott Spark WC race bike check\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/17151103/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-clean-crankset-.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/17151103/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-clean-crankset--297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/17151103/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-clean-crankset--800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/17151103/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-clean-crankset--120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/17151103/Scott-SRAM-Spark-Lars-Forester-Bike-clean-crankset--768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>The race bike is one of the new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/09/2022-scott-spark-gets-bold-new-redesign-as-a-slack-fast-fully-integrated-120mm-xc-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Scott Spark RC World Cup AXS</a> builds with 120mm of travel from the hidden rear shock.</p><ul><li>Frame: SCOTT SPARK 120mm TRAVEL</li><li>Fork: ROCKSHOX SID ULTIMATE RD3 AIR/ BLACKBOX RACE DAY DAMPER 3 MODE, 120MM TRAVEL, 44MM OFFSET</li><li>Rear Shock: ROCKSHOX NUDE 5 RLC3 TRUNNION, 45MM LOCKOUT-TRACTION-DESCEND M